<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>BDSM Long-Distance Preferences Survey</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont@2.44.0/tabler-icons.min.css">
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --bg:#ffffff;--bg2:#f7f7f5;--bg3:#efefec;
  --text:#1a1a1a;--text2:#666;--text3:#aaa;
  --border:rgba(0,0,0,0.10);--border2:rgba(0,0,0,0.20);--border3:rgba(0,0,0,0.38);
  --green:#1e6e34;--green-bg:#edfbf1;
  --r:8px;--rl:12px;
}
@media(prefers-color-scheme:dark){:root{
  --bg:#1c1c1c;--bg2:#272727;--bg3:#313131;
  --text:#e4e4e4;--text2:#999;--text3:#555;
  --border:rgba(255,255,255,0.10);--border2:rgba(255,255,255,0.20);--border3:rgba(255,255,255,0.38);
  --green:#4ade80;--green-bg:#0d2e19;
}}
body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif;background:var(--bg3);color:var(--text);min-height:100vh;line-height:1.6}
.wrap{max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px 16px 100px}

/* lang toggle */
.lang-row{display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:center;margin-bottom:20px}
.lang-btn{padding:5px 14px;border:0.5px solid var(--border2);border-radius:var(--r);background:transparent;cursor:pointer;font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);font-family:inherit;transition:all .15s}
.lang-btn.active{background:var(--bg2);color:var(--text);border-color:var(--border3)}

/* header */
.survey-title{font-size:22px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:6px}
.survey-sub{font-size:14px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:20px}
.prog-wrap{height:3px;background:var(--border);border-radius:2px;margin-bottom:28px;overflow:hidden}
.prog-bar{height:100%;background:var(--text);border-radius:2px;transition:width .3s}

/* sections */
.sec-block{margin-bottom:28px}
.sec-head{font-size:15px;font-weight:500;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;color:var(--text)}
.sec-icon{font-size:16px;color:var(--text2)}

/* question card */
.q-card{background:var(--bg);border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--rl);padding:14px 16px;margin-bottom:10px;transition:border-color .15s}
.q-card:hover{border-color:var(--border2)}
.q-top{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;margin-bottom:10px}
.q-num{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);min-width:18px;padding-top:3px;flex-shrink:0}
.q-text{font-size:14px;color:var(--text);line-height:1.5;flex:1}
.q-info-btn{width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;border:0.5px solid var(--border2);background:transparent;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;transition:all .15s;padding:0}
.q-info-btn:hover{background:var(--bg2);border-color:var(--border3)}
.q-info-btn i{font-size:11px;color:var(--text2)}
.q-tooltip{display:none;margin:0 0 10px 26px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);background:var(--bg2);border-radius:var(--r);padding:8px 12px;line-height:1.5;border-left:2px solid var(--border2)}
.q-tooltip.open{display:block}

/* rating */
.rating-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-left:26px}
.rl{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);min-width:20px}
.rl.right{text-align:right}
input[type=range]{flex:1;height:4px;-webkit-appearance:none;appearance:none;background:var(--border);border-radius:2px;outline:none;cursor:pointer}
input[type=range]::-webkit-slider-thumb{-webkit-appearance:none;width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--text);border:2px solid var(--bg);cursor:pointer}
input[type=range]::-moz-range-thumb{width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--text);border:2px solid var(--bg);cursor:pointer;border:none}
.r-val{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;min-width:20px;text-align:center}

/* note */
.note-toggle{font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;margin:8px 0 0 26px;border:none;background:none;padding:0;font-family:inherit;transition:color .15s}
.note-toggle:hover{color:var(--text2)}
.note-area{margin:6px 0 0 26px;display:none}
.note-area.open{display:block}
.note-row{display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:flex-start}
textarea{flex:1;border:0.5px solid var(--border2);border-radius:var(--r);padding:8px 10px;font-size:13px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--text);background:var(--bg2);resize:vertical;min-height:56px;line-height:1.5;transition:border-color .15s}
textarea:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--border3)}
.mic-btn{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;border:0.5px solid var(--border2);background:var(--bg2);cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--text2);flex-shrink:0;transition:all .15s}
.mic-btn:hover{background:var(--bg3)}
.mic-btn.recording{background:#fef2f2;border-color:#fca5a5;color:#b91c1c;animation:pulse 1s infinite}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.6}}

/* comm */
.comm-card{background:var(--bg);border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--rl);padding:14px 16px;margin-bottom:10px}
.comm-label{font-size:14px;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:10px}
.comm-opts{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px}
.comm-opt{padding:5px 14px;border:0.5px solid var(--border2);border-radius:20px;font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--text2);background:transparent;transition:all .15s;font-family:inherit}
.comm-opt.sel{background:var(--bg2);border-color:var(--border3);color:var(--text)}

/* open */
.open-card{background:var(--bg);border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--rl);padding:14px 16px;margin-bottom:10px}
.open-label{font-size:14px;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:8px}
.open-row{display:flex;gap:6px;align-items:flex-start}
.open-ta{width:100%;border:0.5px solid var(--border2);border-radius:var(--r);padding:8px 10px;font-size:13px;font-family:inherit;color:var(--text);background:var(--bg2);min-height:72px;resize:vertical;line-height:1.5}
.open-ta:focus{outline:none;border-color:var(--border3)}

/* fixed bar */
.fixed-bar{position:fixed;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;background:var(--bg);border-top:0.5px solid var(--border);padding:12px 16px;z-index:100}
.fixed-bar-inner{max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:flex-end}
.btn{padding:9px 20px;border-radius:var(--r);font-size:14px;font-family:inherit;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s}
.btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--text2);border:0.5px solid var(--border2)}
.btn-ghost:hover{border-color:var(--border3);color:var(--text)}
.btn-primary{background:var(--text);color:var(--bg);border:none;font-weight:500}
.btn-primary:hover{opacity:.83}
.btn-primary:disabled{opacity:.45;cursor:default}

/* results */
.res-header{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:24px}
.res-title{font-size:22px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:4px}
.res-meta{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2)}
.res-actions{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center}
.sort-btn{padding:7px 12px;border:0.5px solid var(--border2);border-radius:var(--r);background:var(--bg2);color:var(--text2);font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;white-space:nowrap;transition:all .15s}
.sort-btn:hover{border-color:var(--border3);color:var(--text)}
.share-btn{padding:7px 12px;border:0.5px solid var(--border2);border-radius:var(--r);background:var(--bg2);color:var(--text2);font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;white-space:nowrap;transition:all .15s}
.share-btn:hover{border-color:var(--border3);color:var(--text)}
.translate-bar{background:var(--bg2);border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--r);padding:10px 14px;margin-bottom:20px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.translate-status{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2)}
.res-sec{margin-bottom:24px}
.res-sec-title{font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);padding-bottom:8px;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border);margin-bottom:12px}
.res-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border)}
.res-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.res-qtext{font-size:13px;color:var(--text);flex:1;line-height:1.4}
.res-note{font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);margin-top:3px;font-style:italic}
.res-note-tr{font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:2px;font-style:italic}
.score-wrap{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;min-width:68px;padding-top:2px}
.score-bar-bg{width:44px;height:4px;background:var(--border);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden}
.score-bar{height:100%;border-radius:2px;background:var(--text)}
.score-num{font-size:13px;font-weight:500;min-width:16px;text-align:right}
.score-high{color:var(--green)}
.open-ans{font-size:13px;color:var(--text);background:var(--bg2);border-radius:var(--r);padding:8px 10px;margin-top:4px;line-height:1.5}
.open-ans-tr{font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);background:var(--bg3);border-radius:var(--r);padding:6px 10px;margin-top:4px;line-height:1.5;font-style:italic}
.export-row{display:flex;gap:10px;margin-top:20px;flex-wrap:wrap}

/* shared result banner */
.shared-banner{background:var(--green-bg);border:0.5px solid var(--green);border-radius:var(--r);padding:10px 14px;margin-bottom:20px;font-size:13px;color:var(--green);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}

/* toast */
.toast{position:fixed;bottom:72px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);background:var(--text);color:var(--bg);padding:8px 20px;border-radius:20px;font-size:13px;opacity:0;transition:opacity .25s;pointer-events:none;z-index:999;white-space:nowrap}
.toast.show{opacity:1}

/* mic status */
.mic-status{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:4px;min-height:14px}
.mic-status.active{color:#b91c1c}

/* readonly results */
.view-only-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);background:var(--bg2);border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;padding:3px 10px;margin-left:10px;vertical-align:middle}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

<!-- SURVEY VIEW -->
<div id="vSurvey">
  <div class="lang-row">
    <i class="ti ti-language" style="font-size:16px;color:var(--text2)" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    <button class="lang-btn active" onclick="setLang('en')" id="btnEn">English</button>
    <button class="lang-btn" onclick="setLang('zh')" id="btnZh">中文</button>
  </div>
  <h1 class="survey-title" id="sTitle">BDSM Long-Distance Preferences</h1>
  <p class="survey-sub" id="sSub">Rate your interest (1–10) for each activity. Tap <i class="ti ti-info-circle" style="font-size:13px"></i> for a description. Add notes or use voice input. 0 = not applicable.</p>
  <div class="prog-wrap"><div class="prog-bar" id="progBar" style="width:0%"></div></div>
  <div id="sectCont"></div>
</div>

<!-- RESULTS VIEW -->
<div id="vResults" style="display:none">
  <div class="lang-row">
    <i class="ti ti-language" style="font-size:16px;color:var(--text2)" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    <button class="lang-btn active" onclick="setLang('en')" id="rBtnEn">English</button>
    <button class="lang-btn" onclick="setLang('zh')" id="rBtnZh">中文</button>
  </div>
  <div id="sharedBanner" style="display:none"></div>
  <div class="res-header">
    <div>
      <h1 class="res-title" id="rTitle">Your Preferences Summary</h1>
      <p class="res-meta" id="rMeta"></p>
    </div>
    <div class="res-actions">
      <button class="sort-btn" onclick="toggleSort()" id="sortBtn"><i class="ti ti-arrows-sort" aria-hidden="true"></i><span id="sortLbl">Original order</span></button>
      <button class="share-btn" onclick="shareResults()" id="shareBtn"><i class="ti ti-link" aria-hidden="true"></i><span id="shareLbl">Share</span></button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="translate-bar" id="trBar">
    <span class="translate-status" id="trStatus">Notes will be translated when you switch language</span>
    <button class="btn btn-ghost" style="padding:6px 14px;font-size:13px" onclick="runTranslation()" id="trBtn">Translate notes</button>
  </div>
  <div id="resCont"></div>
  <div class="export-row" id="exportRow" style="display:none">
    <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick="goBack()" id="rBack">← Edit responses</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="exportText()" id="rExport">Copy as text</button>
  </div>
</div>

</div><!-- /wrap -->

<!-- fixed submit bar -->
<div class="fixed-bar" id="fixedBar">
  <div class="fixed-bar-inner">
    <button class="btn btn-ghost" onclick="clearAll()" id="btnClear">Clear all</button>
    <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="showResults()" id="btnSubmit">View results →</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="toast" id="toast"></div>

<script>
// ─── DATA ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
const SECTIONS = [
  {id:'power',icon:'ti-crown',en:'Power Exchange & Authority',zh:'權力交換與支配',questions:[
    {en:'Commanding you to perform non-sexual tasks',zh:'命令你執行非性相關任務',info_en:'Being given instructions to complete everyday tasks (chores, exercise, schedules) as an expression of the power dynamic.',info_zh:'被要求完成日常任務（家務、運動、行程安排）作為權力關係的體現。'},
    {en:'Me choosing what you wear',zh:'由我決定你的穿著',info_en:'Your partner selects your outfit for the day — an intimate form of control over your physical presentation.',info_zh:'由對方選擇你當天的穿著——一種對你外表呈現的親密掌控形式。'},
    {en:'Me choosing your hairstyle, makeup, or accessories',zh:'由我決定你的髮型、妝容或配件',info_en:'Extending appearance control beyond clothing to hair, makeup, or jewelry choices.',info_zh:'將外觀掌控延伸至髮型、妝容或飾品的選擇。'},
    {en:'Wearing a symbolic item representing our dynamic',zh:'佩戴象徵我們關係的物品',info_en:'A collar, bracelet, ring, or other item worn as a private symbol of the D/s relationship.',info_zh:'佩戴項圈、手環、戒指或其他物品作為D/s關係的私人象徵。'},
    {en:'Asking permission before certain activities',zh:'在某些活動前需要請求許可',info_en:'Checking in before eating, going out, sleeping, or other agreed activities to reinforce the authority structure.',info_zh:'在進食、外出、就寢或其他約定的活動前先行請示，強化權威結構。'},
    {en:'Having rules you are expected to follow daily',zh:'每天需要遵守的規則',info_en:'A set of agreed rules governing daily behavior — e.g. posture, language, morning routines.',info_zh:'一套規範日常行為的約定規則——例如姿態、用語、晨間例程。'},
    {en:'Being assigned responsibilities or duties by me',zh:'由我分配職責或任務',info_en:'Regular duties or obligations given by the dominant that the submissive is expected to fulfill.',info_zh:'由主導者指派的定期職責或義務，服從者須負責完成。'},
    {en:'Referring to me with a title or honorific',zh:'以稱謂或尊稱稱呼我',info_en:'Addressing your partner as Sir, Ma\'am, Daddy, Mistress, etc. to mark the power dynamic in conversation.',info_zh:'以大人、媽咪、爸爸、女王等稱謂稱呼對方，在對話中體現權力關係。'},
    {en:'Reporting to me at specific times during the day',zh:'在一天中特定時間向我彙報',info_en:'Scheduled check-ins where you update your partner on what you\'re doing, thinking, or feeling.',info_zh:'定時向對方彙報你的行動、想法或感受。'},
    {en:'Having a formal dominant/submissive dynamic',zh:'建立正式的主/服從關係',info_en:'A clearly defined D/s relationship with agreed roles, expectations, and protocols.',info_zh:'明確定義D/s關係，包含約定的角色、期待和禮儀。'},
    {en:'Fantasies where I have complete control over your actions',zh:'幻想我完全掌控你的行動和決定',info_en:'Erotic or emotional fantasies involving total obedience and surrender of decision-making.',info_zh:'涉及完全服從和放棄決策權的情慾或情感幻想。'},
    {en:'Giving me authority over parts of your daily routine',zh:'將日常作息的部分權力交給我',info_en:'Surrendering control over specific areas like sleep schedule, diet, or exercise to your partner.',info_zh:'將特定領域（如睡眠時程、飲食、運動）的控制權交給對方。'},
    {en:'Being corrected when you break rules',zh:'違反規則時被糾正',info_en:'Receiving verbal correction, a reminder, or a consequence when an agreed rule is not followed.',info_zh:'未遵守約定規則時接受言語糾正、提醒或後果。'},
    {en:'Receiving praise for obedience',zh:'因服從而獲得稱讚',info_en:'"Good girl/boy" moments — positive reinforcement that rewards compliance and pleasing behavior.',info_zh:'「乖女孩/乖男孩」時刻——獎勵服從和取悅行為的正向強化。'},
    {en:'Temporary "24/7" style power exchange dynamics',zh:'臨時性「24/7」式權力交換',info_en:'Time-limited periods (a weekend, a week) where the power dynamic is in effect around the clock.',info_zh:'限時期間（一個週末、一週）全天候實行權力交換關係。'},
    {en:'Giving you a daily routine or ritual',zh:'給你每日例程或儀式',info_en:'A structured plan for your day set by your partner — morning rituals, tasks, check-in times.',info_zh:'由對方設定的每日結構化計畫——晨間儀式、任務、回報時間。'},
    {en:'Assigning recurring tasks or responsibilities',zh:'分配定期任務或職責',info_en:'Ongoing assignments that repeat weekly or daily, building consistency in the dynamic.',info_zh:'每週或每日重複的持續性任務，建立關係的一致性。'},
    {en:'Reporting details of your day to me',zh:'向我彙報你的每日細節',info_en:'Sharing a detailed account of your day — activities, emotions, interactions — for the dominant to review.',info_zh:'分享你一天的詳細記錄——活動、情緒、互動——供主導者查閱。'},
    {en:'Check-ins at specific times',zh:'在特定時間回報',info_en:'Mandatory messages or calls at set times (morning, lunch, bedtime) to maintain connection and structure.',info_zh:'在固定時間（早晨、午餐、就寢）強制傳訊或通話，維持聯繫和結構。'},
    {en:'Using titles (Sir, Daddy, Mistress, etc.)',zh:'使用稱謂（大人、爸爸、女王等）',info_en:'Consistently addressing your partner with a chosen honorific as part of your established dynamic.',info_zh:'持續以選定的尊稱稱呼對方，作為已建立關係的一部分。'},
    {en:'Formal rules or protocols',zh:'正式規則或禮儀',info_en:'Specific etiquette or behavior codes — how to speak, how to address your dominant, posture rules.',info_zh:'特定的禮儀或行為規範——說話方式、稱呼主導者的方式、姿態規則。'},
    {en:'Being punished for disobedience',zh:'因不服從而受到懲罰',info_en:'Agreed consequences for breaking rules — tasks, restrictions, or other sanctions negotiated in advance.',info_zh:'違反規則的約定後果——事先協商好的任務、限制或其他制裁。'},
    {en:'Creating a point-based reward and punishment system',zh:'建立積分制獎懲系統',info_en:'A gamified tracking system where good behavior earns points toward rewards and violations deduct points.',info_zh:'遊戲化的追蹤系統，良好行為積分換取獎勵，違規則扣分。'},
  ]},
  {id:'service',icon:'ti-list-check',en:'Service & Rituals',zh:'服從與儀式',questions:[
    {en:'Completing regular tasks assigned by me',zh:'完成我分配的定期任務',info_en:'Structured assignments (cleaning, journaling, exercise) given by your partner that you are expected to complete.',info_zh:'由對方給予的結構化任務（清潔、日記、運動），你須完成這些任務。'},
    {en:'Daily check-ins or accountability tasks',zh:'每日回報或問責任務',info_en:'Short daily rituals confirming you\'ve completed your obligations — a text, photo, or voice note.',info_zh:'確認你已完成義務的簡短每日儀式——文字、照片或語音訊息。'},
