    {en:'Having morning or bedtime rituals',zh:'有早晨或就寢儀式',info_en:'Set routines that begin or end each day — affirmations, check-ins, specific behaviors.',info_zh:'開始或結束每天的固定例程——肯定語、回報、特定行為。'},
